Authority for interstate compacts emanates from the United States Constitution. 54 The grant of

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
AND

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
preempts or conflicts with federal law, then congressional consent is imperative. 68

