==== Private funding crushes fusion research ====

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
(% class=&amp;#34;StyleStyleBold12pt&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-size:13.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&amp;#34; %)Razani 12(%%) (Rezwan, Executive Director – Focus Fusion Society, “Fusion Finance Conversation:  An Invitation”, Fusion Energy League, 4-14, http:~~/~~/www.fusionenergyleague.org/index.php/blog/article/f usion_finance_conversatiourl:http://www.fusionenergyleague.org/index.php/blog/article/f%20usion_finance_conversation_invitation)

